org.osgi.service.onem2m.dto

Enum ReleaseVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ReleaseVersion>
      • org.osgi.service.onem2m.dto.ReleaseVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ReleaseVersion>

    public enum ReleaseVersion
extends Enum<ReleaseVersion>
    enum expresses oneM2M specification version.

    This information is introduced after Release 2.0 and oneM2M uses only R2A, R3_0 (as 2a and 3).

    See Also:
    oneM2M XSD releaseVersion
